<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
    <meta name="keywords" content="공모주, IPO, 청약, 주식, 캘린더, 일정">
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site_url }}">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{ title }}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{ description }}">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site_url }}">
    <meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR">
    <meta property="og:image" content="{{ og_image_url }}">
    
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0066cc">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="og-image.png">

    <!-- Twitter Card -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ title }}">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ description }}">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="{{ og_image_url }}">

    <script type="application/ld+json">
        {{ structured_data | safe }}
    </script>
    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-G8EY2E5T71"></script>
    <script>
      window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
      function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
      gtag('js', new Date());
      gtag('config', 'G-G8EY2E5T71');
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Google AdSense -->
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3746587025439528"
     crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>공모주 캘린더</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">대한민국 IPO 청약 일정</p>
        </header>


        <div class="ad-banner" role="region" aria-label="광고">
            <!-- gong-mo -->
            <ins class="adsbygoogle"
                 style="display:block"
                 data-ad-client="ca-pub-3746587025439528"
                 data-ad-slot="7570903568"
                 data-ad-format="auto"
                 data-full-width-responsive="false"></ins>
            <script>
                 (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
            </script>
        </div>

        <section class="calendar-section">
            <iframe src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=87a9feb0d01485564f1c4267d63b46ec329c3cb45c089f129a1c8edc546931cf%40group.calendar.google.com&ctz=Asia%2FSeoul&mode=MONTH&showTitle=0&showNav=1&showDate=1&showPrint=0&showTabs=1&showCalendars=0&showTz=0"
                    style="border: 0"
                    width="100%"
                    height="600"
                    frameborder="0"
                    scrolling="no">
            </iframe>
        <section class="subscribe-section" style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <div class="button-group">
                <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0?cid=ODdhOWZlYjBkMDE0ODU1NjRmMWM0MjY3ZDYzYjQ2ZWMzMjljM2NiNDVjMDg5ZjEyOWExYzhlZGM1NDY5MzFjZkBncm91cC5jYWxlbmRhci5nb29nbGUuY29t"
                   class="subscribe-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                    + Google 캘린더에 추가
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="update-info" style="display: block; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #5f6368; box-shadow: none; background: transparent; padding: 0;">
                <span class="label">마지막 업데이트:</span>
                <span id="last-updated">-</span>
            </div>
        </section>
        </section>


        <section class="ipo-list-section">
            <h2>청약 일정 목록</h2>
            <div class="filter-controls" id="filter-controls">
                <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="upcoming">다가오는 일정</button>
                <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="all">전체</button>
            </div>
            <div id="ipo-list" class="ipo-list">
                <p class="loading">데이터를 불러오는 중...</p>
                <!-- 인피드 광고 영역 (5번째 항목 위치) -->
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer>
        <div class="ad-banner-bottom" role="region" aria-label="광고">
            <!-- gong-mo-bottom -->
            <ins class="adsbygoogle"
                 style="display:block"
                 data-ad-client="ca-pub-3746587025439528"
                 data-ad-slot="4370025151"
                 data-ad-format="auto"
                 data-full-width-responsive="false"></ins>
            <script>
                 (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
            </script>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            데이터를 가져온 <a href="http://www.38.co.kr" class="footer-source-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">38커뮤니케이션 바로가기</a>
            <p class="footer-disclaimer">본 서비스는 38커뮤니케이션과는 별개로 운영되는 서비스입니다.</p>
        </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
